extensions.description: Your go-to n8n agent marketplace powered by x402. Buy / Sell and rent agents with pay-per-use.

The $GIG token is the heart of Gig-Space.com, a decentralised ecosystem built to fuel the growing gig economy.
Built on Solana, $GIG connects freelancers, contractors, and businesses through seamless on-chain payments, rewards, and growth incentives. Gig-Space.com is creating a new way to work, earn, and collaborate.
This is more than a token, it’s the foundation of the next generation of online hiring.
